?mpg
student = c("A","B","C","D","E")
Xgpa = c(3.2,2.7,2.5,3.4,2.2)
Xage = c(22,27,24,28,23)
Ystatescore = c(550,570,525,670,490)
cor_gpa_score = cor(Xgpa, Ystatescore) #rx1y
cor_age_score = cor(Xage, Ystatescore) #rx2y

det_gpa_score = (cor_gpa_score ^ 2) #r^2x1y
det_age_score = (cor_age_score ^ 2) #r^2x2y


LMXgpaY = lm(Ystatescore ~ Xgpa)

LMXageY = lm(Ystatescore ~ Xage)
par(mfrow=c(1,2))

plot(Ystatescore ~ Xgpa)
abline(LMXgpaY)
text(x=2.6,
     y=630,
     paste("cor:",round(cor_gpa_score,2)),
     cex = 0.7)

plot(Ystatescore ~ Xage)
abline(LMXageY)
text(paste(cor_age_score))
text(x=25,
     y=630,
     paste("cor:",round(cor_age_score,2)),
     cex = 0.5)

class_multireg = lm(Ystatescore ~ Xgpa + Xage)
class_multireg
## 
## Call:
## lm(formula = Ystatescore ~ Xgpa + Xage)
## 
## Coefficients:
## (Intercept)         Xgpa         Xage  
##      -44.81        87.64        14.53
class_pred_Y = (class_multireg$coefficients[1]) + (class_multireg$coefficients[2] * Xgpa) + (class_multireg$coefficients[3] * Xage)

class_pred_Y
## [1] 555.3637 584.2085 523.0816 660.0896 482.2566

                            Xage,
                            Ystatescore,
                            round(class_pred_Y,0))
